documentation.text: The WarpVaultSCFactory contract is designed to produce individual WarpVaultLP contracts*
The WarpVaultSCFactory contract is designed to produce individual WarpVaultLP contracts*

params._InterestRate: is the address of the InterestRateModel contract created for this Warp Vault
params._StableCoin: is the address of the stablecoin contract this WarpVault will manage
params._initialExchangeRate: is the exchange rate mantissa used to determine the initial exchange rate of stablecoin to warp stablecoin
params._timelock: is a variable representing the number of seconds the timeWizard will prevent withdraws and borrows from a contracts(one week is 605800 seconds)*
params._warpTeam: is the address of the Warp Team used for fees

createNewWarpVaultSC(address,address,add.notice: createNewWarpVaultSC is used to create new WarpVaultSC contract instances
